++## 3. Decision families covered
++
++The runtime-shaped traces cover:
++- `REUSE`
++- `REUSE_WITH_WARNING`
++- `RECOMPUTE`
++- `REFUSE`
++
++Across the two logical twins:
++- `COMPLIANCE`
++- `ADVISORY`
++
++---
++
